'''Pummelstaves''' were [[Melee weapon/Legends|melee weapons]] used by the technophobic [[Red Knights of Life]]. They were tubes of wrought [[Iron/Legends|iron]], and were employed at a close range.<ref name="VP">''[[The New Jedi Order: Vector Prime]]''</ref>

During the Red Knights' uprising on [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]] in [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], several members of the organization used pummelstaves to wreck a [[Dressellian/Legends|Dressellian's]] [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]], advising [[Gender/Legends|him]] to either ride an animal such as a [[tutakan]], or walk as nature intended.<ref name="VP" />

